{"tid":2372618,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有關人類智能與危險性的關係","createTime":"2021-01-19T23:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T07:44:14.000Z","uid":47901,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8d97dd736dc4044dca6b9a5ce8ee83c3f35ecfb6","tid":2372618,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T23:32:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Wuf0-x9Pbu4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWuf0-x9Pbu4&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmeo%2FVxAEwmAwDimrVtn2syv4%3D&h=a3f7cdb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Wuf0-x9Pbu4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hz58S7r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhz58S7r.png&h=ff29da8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我話既，中等智力的人，多數是最具危險性，同對社會危害性最大的人<br />\n<br />\n因為，這些人絕對有謀生，謀利的精密思考能力，而且會傾向在其生命週期之中，將之發揮同optimize到極致，我稱之為&ldquo;精叻&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n但，卻比較難達到形而上的抽象思考能力，而呢種能力通常會導致啟蒙，覺醒境界，到達此境界，就是一條直去而不回頭的路<br />\n<br />\n例如牛頓，保羅，德蘭修女，六祖慧能等等"},{"pid":"b9a93df3d5cc765a94d0ae822f79a8fd0262d2eb","tid":2372618,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T23:33:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/b3oi174RAiI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fb3oi174RAiI&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmeo%2FVxAEwmAwDimrVtn2syv4%3D&h=30d37c91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/b3oi174RAiI</a>"},{"pid":"a3011417de1001e6811823bf01faee8253080067","tid":2372618,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"8d97dd736dc4044dca6b9a5ce8ee83c3f35ecfb6","tid":2372618,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T23:32:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Wuf0-x9Pbu4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWuf0-x9Pbu4&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmeo%2FVxAEwmAwDimrVtn2syv4%3D&h=a3f7cdb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Wuf0-x9Pbu4</a><br